    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――現在",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あの時は、結局日が暮れるまで踊る羽目になって\n物凄く困ったんだからな……",
      "startTime": 6.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}君、途中から\nすっかり息が上がってたよね。運動不足じゃない？",
      "startTime": 9.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "振り付けも途中から崩れちゃってたし\n今度、僕が手取り足取り教えてあげるよ",
      "startTime": 16.4788886318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "絶対筋肉痛になるから遠慮するよ\nそれと、いきなり外で踊るのももう勘弁してくれ……",
      "startTime": 23.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、考えておくよ\nそんなことより、さっきも言ったよね",
      "startTime": 29.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "あの日、君と広場で踊ったじゃない？\nそれが今回の舞台演出に繋がったんだ",
      "startTime": 36.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あれがどんな風に繋がるんだ？\n全然見当がつかないんだが……",
      "startTime": 42.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "テーマは、『ダンスは楽しい\nみんなで踊れば、もっと楽しい』だよ",
      "startTime": 48.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスの振り付けに注目してほしいな\n後は、ステージを観るまでのお楽しみだ",
      "startTime": 55.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、そろそろ行ってくるよ\nまた一緒に踊ろう。この間の続きだ",
      "startTime": 61.1999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、行ってらっしゃい。……また一緒に踊る？\nこの間の続き？　……どういう意味だ？",
      "startTime": 69.5538384595,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2059.5694067000068,
          "startTime": 66.6999994914
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3526.2360732999978,
          "startTime": 68.166666158
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5749.403222300003,
          "startTime": 75.3032416818
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livehousemiddle-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "ハロー、アメリカのみんな、君達の応援のおかげで\nまたこの国に来られたよ。ありがとう",
      "startTime": 81.0666646321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7544.7782358999975,
          "startTime": 83.6480199177
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "この国は今の僕ら――\n四人体制のLizNoirの、始まりの場所なんだ",
      "startTime": 87.5666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "ここには辛い思い出も、楽しかった思い出も沢山ある\nその全部が、今の僕らを作り上げたんだ",
      "startTime": 97.8666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "さて、今から歌う新曲には\n即興でも出来る振り付けを入れてある",
      "startTime": 105.4666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "あ、日本語で言っても伝わらないかな\nそれじゃ……Let's dance",
      "startTime": 111.7999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "We are LizNoir\nand...You are LizNoir！",
      "startTime": 117.0999979655,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4896.745093999996,
          "startTime": 119.966666158
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "これが、さっき葵が言っていた振り付けか……\n確かにこれなら俺でも出来るし、凄くキャッチーだ",
      "startTime": 125.0333292643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "会場の一体感が凄いな。俺まで踊り出したくなってきた\n『また一緒に踊ろう』って……そうか、このことか",
      "startTime": 135.5666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "僕はダンスが好きな井川葵のままだよ\nBIG4になっても、変わっていない",
      "startTime": 145.1247756635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、ああ言ったけど……葵は変わったよ\n以前は、ただ踊るのが好きなだけだったけど……",
      "startTime": 153.5999766031,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今は、みんなとダンスを楽しめるようになった\n……凄いアイドルになったな、葵",
      "startTime": 162.5666432697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "（やっぱり楽しいな、ダンスは）\n（言葉が通じなくても、全身で通じ合えるから）",
      "startTime": 169.5999664305,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoir海外ツアー　追加公演終了後",
      "startTime": 174.8210119082,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi016.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの、急に呼び出したりなんかして\n僕に緊急の話って何？　新しい仕事？",
      "startTime": 180.3333048502,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 12.304640199999994,
          "startTime": 177.4333206176
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 176.8666539509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "残念だけど違う。……葵、俺のスマホを見てくれ\nこのニュース、知ってるか？",
      "startTime": 189.5333048502,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4145.622206100001,
          "startTime": 188.5999715168
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi017.m4a",
      "text": "どれどれ……『日本のアイドル、LizNoir所属の\n井川葵、アメリカで単独ゲリラライブを実施』……",
      "startTime": 196.6537227825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "ツアーファイナルのステージが終わった直後に\n踊り足りないからって、外の広場で踊っただろ",
      "startTime": 204.3666381835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "そうしたら人が集まって来て、みんな踊り出して……\nあの時、海外のメディアに写真を撮られてたんだよ",
      "startTime": 212.5666381835,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_12_03-aoi018.m4a",
      "text": "へぇ、海外メディアがニュースに取り上げてくれたんだ\nみんな笑顔で、凄くいい写真だね",
      "startTime": 220.2999715168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
